item.g:title: DART-6UL Evaluation Kits
item.g:description: The DART-6UL evaluation kits are based on the DART-6UL System on Module, powered by NXP i.MX 6ULL processor. The DART-6UL Development Kit and Starter Kit can serve as a complete development platform for both evaluation and application development purposes. The kits provide a great showcase of the DART-6UL connectivity features and performance.
